22  package com.github.talbotgui.psl.socle.adminpsl.apiclient.api;
23  
24  import org.springframework.http.MediaType;
25  import org.springframework.web.bind.annotation.GetMapping;
26  import org.springframework.web.bind.annotation.PathVariable;
27  import org.springframework.web.bind.annotation.PostMapping;
28  import org.springframework.web.bind.annotation.RequestBody;
29  
30  import com.github.talbotgui.psl.socle.adminpsl.apiclient.dto.RequeteRechercheTransfertsDto;
31  import com.github.talbotgui.psl.socle.adminpsl.apiclient.dto.ResultatRechercheTransfertsDto;
32  import com.github.talbotgui.psl.socle.commun.apiclient.dto.Page;
33  import com.github.talbotgui.psl.socle.commun.utils.RegexUtils;
34  
35  import io.swagger.v3.oas.annotations.security.SecurityRequirement;
36  import jakarta.validation.Valid;
37  import jakarta.validation.constraints.Min;
38  import jakarta.validation.constraints.Pattern;
39  
40  public interface AdminPslTransfertAPI {
41  
42  	/** URI de génération de soumissions en masse. */
43  	public static final String URI_GENERATION_TRANSFERTS = AdminPslAPI.URI_BASE + "/genererDesTransferts/{nbTransferts}";
44  
45  	/** URI des détails d'un transfert. */
46  	public static final String URI_TRANSFERT_DETAILS = AdminPslAPI.URI_BASE + "/transfert/{idTransfert}";
47  
48  	/** URI de la liste des transferts via une recherche multi-critères. */
49  	public static final String URI_TRANSFERT_LISTE = AdminPslAPI.URI_BASE + "/transfert";
50  
51  	@GetMapping(URI_TRANSFERT_DETAILS)
52  	Object chargerDetailsDunTransfert(@Pattern(regexp = RegexUtils.ID) @PathVariable("idTransert") String idTransert);
53  
54  	@GetMapping(URI_GENERATION_TRANSFERTS)
55  	void genererDesTeledossiers(@Min(0) @PathVariable("nbTransferts") int nbTransferts);
56  
57  	@SecurityRequirement(name = "bearer-admin")
58  	@PostMapping(value = URI_TRANSFERT_LISTE, consumes = MediaType.APPLICATION_JSON_VALUE, produces = MediaType.APPLICATION_JSON_VALUE)
59  	Page<ResultatRechercheTransfertsDto> rechercherDesTeledossiers(@Valid @RequestBody RequeteRechercheTransfertsDto parametresRecherche);
60  
61  }
